OL,3,CThames Water lenders consider offering
OL,4,C'golden share' to avert nationalisation
OL,6,FThames Water's lenders have revealed
OL,7,Fthey are looking at offering a "golden
OL,8,Fshare" to the Government as part of a
OL,9,Frevised rescue deal to stave off
OL,10,Fnationalisation of the stricken
OL,11,Fsupplier.
OL,13,FThe consortium of lenders bidding for
OL,14,Fthe UK's biggest water firm, which has
OL,15,Faround 16 million customers across
OL,16,FLondon and the South East, said it
OL,17,Fremains in talks with regulators over
OL,18,Fa possible deal, with "material
OL,19,Fimprovements" being considered on its
OL,20,Fprevious #10 billion proposal to
OL,21,Fappease government concerns.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@FO]zD@WOU{D@MO]
