OL,3,CThames Water lenders consider offering
OL,4,C'golden share' to avert nationalisation
OL,6,FIt comes amid reports Andy Burnham
OL,7,Fcould temporarily nationalise the debt-
OL,8,Fladen company, having already
OL,9,Fsignalled he wants to bring in a 10-
OL,10,Fyear plan to renationalise the water
OL,11,Findustry, saying reform is needed to
OL,12,Fput the public interest first.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
