OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784630877
OL,3,CThames Water lenders consider offering
OL,4,C'golden share' to avert nationalisation
OL,6,FLondon & Valley Water said it
OL,7,F"recognises that the new Government,
OL,8,Fled by Prime Minister Andy Burnham,
OL,9,Fwould like to see water companies
OL,10,Fcreate greater local public control
OL,11,Fand involvement to strengthen
OL,12,Faccountability for protecting
OL,13,Finvestment and delivering
OL,14,Fimprovements".
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
