CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784630877
OL,3,CThames Water lenders consider offering
OL,4,C'golden share' to avert nationalisation
OL,6,FIt added: "The consortium has
OL,7,Fevaluated potential new local public
OL,8,Fcontrol supervisory structures for
OL,9,FThames Water which can be beneficial
OL,10,Fto customers and intends to discuss
OL,11,Fthis with the new Secretary of State,
OL,12,Falongside additional commitments that
OL,13,Fcould be implemented through a 'golden
OL,14,Fshare'."
OL,16,FThe creditors said the new supervisory
OL,17,Fstructure would give "enhanced local
OL,18,Frepresentation for local authorities
OL,19,Fand regional leaders".
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@HO]yD@VOU{D@UO]
