PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784630877
OL,3,CThames Water lenders consider offering
OL,4,C'golden share' to avert nationalisation
OL,6,FThe Government holds golden shares in
OL,7,Fa number of privatised companies of
OL,8,Fnational and strategic importance,
OL,9,Fsuch as Royal Mail following its
OL,10,Ftakeover by EP Group last year.
OL,12,FThese special rights shares give the
OL,13,FSecretary of State the power to veto
OL,14,Fmajor asset sales, foreign takeovers
OL,15,For changes to the company's
OL,16,Finstitution.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
