CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784630877
OL,3,CThames Water lenders consider offering
OL,4,C'golden share' to avert nationalisation
OL,6,FA rescue plan by creditors is seen as
OL,7,Fthe final realistic option to avoid
OL,8,FThames Water being placed into a
OL,9,Fspecial administration regime after a
OL,10,Fprevious rescue deal with US private
OL,11,Fequity giant KKR collapsed in May last
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FBut creditors have already been sent
OL,15,Fback to the drawing board after former
OL,16,Fenvironment secretary Emma Reynolds
OL,17,Flast month warned she did not believe
OL,18,Ftheir #10 billion plan for Thames
OL,19,FWater goes far enough to protect
OL,20,Fcustomers or the environment.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
