PN,37207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784630877
OL,3,CThames Water lenders consider offering
OL,4,C'golden share' to avert nationalisation
OL,6,FFormer farmer minister Dame Angela
OL,7,FEagle was last night appointed as the
OL,8,Fnew Environment Secretary by Mr
OL,9,FBurnham.
OL,11,FA spokesman for London & Valley Water
OL,12,Fsaid: "Thames Water is a company of
OL,13,Fnational importance, and we look
OL,14,Fforward to working with the new
OL,15,FGovernment to secure a long-term
OL,16,Fsolution which delivers greater public
OL,17,Fcontrol and the best outcome for
OL,18,Fcustomers.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
