OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784630877
OL,3,CThames Water lenders consider offering
OL,4,C'golden share' to avert nationalisation
OL,6,F"We continue to believe that the L&VW
OL,7,Fplan is by far the fastest and most
OL,8,Freliable route to solving Thames
OL,9,FWater's complex problems and improving
OL,10,Foutcomes for customers and the
OL,11,Fenvironment, and achieves this without
OL,12,Fany government funding or cost to
OL,13,Ftaxpayers.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
