CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784630877
OL,3,CThames Water lenders consider offering
OL,4,C'golden share' to avert nationalisation
OL,6,F"Under our plan, customers will have
OL,7,Fstrong protections, regulators and
OL,8,Fgovernment will have enhanced
OL,9,Foversight, and there will be greater
OL,10,Fcontrols to ensure Thames Water
OL,11,Fdelivers the record investment needed
OL,12,Fto improve environmental and
OL,13,Foperational performance."
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
